# Forms & Validation

- Shared Zod schemas in `lib/schemas/`; reuse on client (react-hook-form) and server (API/actions).
- Show field-level errors in es-MX; associate `aria-describedby` with inputs.

```typescript
export const checkoutSchema = z.object({
  email: z.string().email(),
  rfc: z.string().regex(/^([A-ZÑ&]{3,4})\d{6}[A-Z0-9]{3}$/i).optional(),
  cp: z.string().regex(/^\d{5}$/),
  phone: z.string().regex(/^\+52\d{10}$/),
});
```

- Disable submit while pending; prevent double-submit on payment forms.
- CRM forms: audit who changed customer RFC or shipping address (`updatedById`).
- Never trust client-only validation for prices, discounts, or inventory.
